metadata.name: Eros
metadata.description:
Feelings and sensibilities do not need to be covered, in this garden death dies, Transient becomes permanent and mortal becomes permanent.
The creature is created and with the miracle of love and thanks to art, a lost paradise is restored this time in the form of the paradise of this world, A paradise with obvious pleasures and in order to satisfy as many bodily desires as possible, pleasures that are not rooted in sin or deceit and debauchery.
